{"tid":1610562,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"100%肯定同大家講，警察開實彈真槍！射市民！射示威者！會再出現同埋合理化！","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:55:07.000Z","uid":112748,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"199a815271eac64f124d383e7e1c45231eb1f2ea","tid":1610562,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:06:41.000Z","msg":"就算唔係民主國家社會，都未必認同警察射殺市民射殺示威者係可以免於刑責之上，驢痿蔥呢條on9被中聯辦魔鬼推出黎，繼續100%幫前線黑警護航，一番解話連小學生都越聽越嬲，係法理同道德都完全沒有一絲歉意，目的只有一個，就係呢個政權非常之需要呢班任意莽為既警察，絕不會懲罰任何跳制既警員，咁跟住會點呢？原來射市民係唔使受罰，只要係射殺既係示威者背景，反政權既就可以，以後都唔使埋身肉搏，又唔使跑，有人沖埋黎我就開槍！又或者無鏡頭影住，我又開槍.............因為最終，一日個政權無變，我就唔使受罰！個個以後會更多警察帶面罩，一槍攪掂一個，唔使上庭即時審判，最重要係可以收到阻嚇作用！<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？驚唔驚？"},{"pid":"5d515de946e75b1da9d84aa0e0047e5160d7d21b","tid":1610562,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:06:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日出過街嘅，就算你係去邊都好，馬上將你社交平台有關嘅Post通訊軟件有關嘅對話全部刪除，最底兩張相有講點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpOJUqj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpOJUqj.png&h=a4723306&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTTt5w0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTTt5w0.png&h=9a32150c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99gCYR1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99gCYR1.png&h=eeed8d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4RO5w2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4RO5w2.png&h=4ef3844c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDBvzqn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDBvzqn.png&h=ca0410f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNE1F5o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/